      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "1074-1102",
      "markText": "七伯大声喊道：“我是忠于党，忠于人民的！我不是投降派！”",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1074&rangeEnd=1102",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1074&rangeEnd=1102"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_17_11159-11184",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "11159-11184",
      "markText": "吴大夫，我这里没有什么事，需要你的人很多，你去吧！",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=11159&rangeEnd=11184",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=11159&rangeEnd=11184"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_10_9823-9886",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "9823-9886",
      "markText": "行军第二天深夜正当进入梦乡，列车突然刹车，重重的“咣当”一下，五六个战友当即被背靠的铁板磕破后脑身亡，还有十多人因脑震荡重伤。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9823&rangeEnd=9886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9823&rangeEnd=9886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_33_21247-21334",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "21247-21334",
      "markText": "何其有幸，让我这一平凡的女孩，经过大量的书籍，透过历史的长河去遇见你。对于你，我有太多的敬仰。即使在有你的年代不曾有我，但庆幸的是在有我的年代依然有你。感谢这土地上曾经有你。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=21247&rangeEnd=21334",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=21247&rangeEnd=21334"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_28_3712-3737",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "3712-3737",
      "markText": "周恩来在“文革”期间胸前始终佩戴“为人民服务”徽章",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=3712&rangeEnd=3737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=3712&rangeEnd=3737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_5_13643-13683",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13643-13683",
      "markText": "后来“历博”派人送来上述文物的复制品，要求原件留存“历博”，便于长期保管、陈列。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13643&rangeEnd=13683",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13643&rangeEnd=13683"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_22_18973-19043",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "18973-19043",
      "markText": "七伯接着说：“凡事要实事求是。她现在这么小，既不会用筷子，也不会拿勺子，手就是她的工具，你怎么能打她呢！要记住，生活中工作中都要实事求是。”",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=18973&rangeEnd=19043",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=18973&rangeEnd=19043"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_16_4508-4568",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "4508-4568",
      "markText": "想不到十三年后，龚澎不幸英年早逝；十六年后，乔冠华又迫于四人帮压力做了对不起周总理的事，七伯逝世时他深为忏悔，扶棺痛哭。",
      "totalCount": 55,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4508&rangeEnd=4568",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4508&rangeEnd=4568"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_29_1696-1786",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "1696-1786",
      "markText": "恩来伯伯这颗伟大的心灵，为了国家和人民，可以入地狱，下火海，可以忍受无边的屈辱和苦难，唯独不能承受的，就是对他革命信仰的践踏，因为，这是他为之奋斗了一生的比生命更加宝贵的事业和理想",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1696&rangeEnd=1786",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=1696&rangeEnd=1786"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_9_3052-3080",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3052-3080",
      "markText": "这是一个经历了千锤百炼的智者对所有的人充满挚爱深情的眼神",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3052&rangeEnd=3080",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3052&rangeEnd=3080"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_5_11578-11627",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "11578-11627",
      "markText": "凡是提及他生父、二伯母（我祖母）包括我父亲的地方，一律空格、抬头；自称“兄”“嫂”时，则列于右侧。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11578&rangeEnd=11627",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=11578&rangeEnd=11627"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_17_7807-7870",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "7807-7870",
      "markText": "不幸的是，1967年6月，柯印华在第四军医大学附属医院住院时，因为医护人员失职，静脉注射发霉的葡萄糖，他不治身亡，年仅25岁。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037709&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=7807&rangeEnd=7870",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a8c32fa0813ab753ag0197d2?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=7807&rangeEnd=7870"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037709_6_3163-3194",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3163-3194",
      "markText": "行事的果断与敏捷有如电闪雷鸣，思考问题的细心与周密有如水银泻地",
